title: Cien Anti-Wrinkle Night Cream with Q10, Hyaluronic Acid and Vitamin E 50ml
description: Cien Anti-Wrinkle Night Cream with Q10, Hyaluronic Acid and Vitamin E 50ml is an Anti-wrinkle night cream. When applied regularly, it helps to reduce the appearance of fine lines. It has Coenzyme Q10 and hyaluronic acid which helps to promote regenerative system of the basal cells of the skin. It is a firming skin cream which helps to promote skin elasticity, luster for younger looking skin. It also helps to hydrate the upper layers of the skin. It also penetrates quickly, to help soothe the skin and which helps to brings a better skin hydration.
